# Advanced HTTP Requests Example

### Authentication Example
# @name login
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json
User-Agent: RuPost/0.1.0
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### Request with Multiple Headers
# @name api-request-with-headers
GET https://httpbin.org/headers
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9
X-Request-ID: req-123-456
X-API-Version: v1
Accept: application/json
Accept-Language: zh-CN,en-US

###

### PUT Request (Update Resource)
# @name update-user
PUT https://httpbin.org/put
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer token123

{
  "id": 42,
  "name": "Alice Updated",
  "email": "alice.new@example.com",
  "profile": {
    "bio": "Software Engineer",
    "location": "San Francisco"
  },
  "tags": ["developer", "rust", "api"]
}

###

### PATCH Request (Partial Update)
# @name partial-update
PATCH https://httpbin.org/patch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newemail@example.com"
}

###

### Request with Form Data
# @name login-form
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=alice&password=secret123&remember=true

###

### Request with Plain Text Body
# @name create-note
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: text/plain

This is a plain text note.
It can span multiple lines.
用户可以使用中文内容。

###

### Complex JSON with Nested Objects
# @name create-order
POST https://httpbin.org/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "ORD-2026-0121-001",
  "customer": {
    "id": 123,
    "name": "Alice Chen",
    "email": "alice@example.com"
  },
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "PROD-001",
      "name": "Laptop",
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 1299.99
    },
    {
      "productId": "PROD-002",
      "name": "Mouse",
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 29.99
    }
  ],
  "shipping": {
    "address": "123 Main St",
    "city": "San Francisco",
    "zipCode": "94102",
    "country": "USA"
  },
  "paymentMethod": "credit_card",
  "total": 1359.97
}

